{"tid":2160971,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"泛民杯葛議會嘅最大好處","createTime":"2020-08-17T09:54:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-11T05:31:05.000Z","uid":108757,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"32652421cdfb51a983af65302c0cca078d4ebf11","tid":2160971,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T09:54:49.000Z","msg":"以往保皇黨最常用就係<span class=\"red\">賴泛民議員拉布、咩都反對，搞到民生唔好</span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n宜家如果泛民全部走，剩低保皇黨，佢地就無得賴。反而<span class=\"red\">泛民可以鬧返保皇黨搞到民生、經濟唔好</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，總之有咩問題賴曬佢地就得，佢地根本無得反擊。<br />\n<br />\n只有議會得返保皇黨，先至凸顯到搞亂香港嘅係政府同保皇黨，到時市民無飯開自然會鬧返保皇黨，而泛民可以完全抽身，甚至落井下石，爭取返游離民意<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，民意唔會嫌多。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">如果泛民賴死唔走，有兩個可能。</span><br />\n一︰泛民<span class=\"red\">繼續議會抗爭</span>、拉布、投反對票<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n保皇黨就<span class=\"red\">繼續將責任賴曬泛民議員</span>，泛民唔會得到中立、淺藍支持。<br />\n二︰泛民<span class=\"red\">唔抗爭、唔做野</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n保皇黨就<span class=\"red\">繼續將責任賴曬泛民議員</span>，泛民唔會得到中立、淺藍支持。<br />\n黃營市民會將矛頭指向泛民，<span class=\"red\">批評點解留係議會咩都唔做，泛民會流失淺黃民意</span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n為免泛民陷進退兩難之局，<span class=\"xx-large\">盡早抽身自立門戶</span>先係明智。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">仲有快撚啲公投！</span></span>"},{"pid":"00b38b6a3db7888dab97145ebd5e184244d2416b","tid":2160971,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T09:58:27.000Z","msg":"賴佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6c0ba81fdb2c5a605d68dc14aca6543d3ad8fc9","tid":2160971,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T10:00:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27ff36da2e39bf562cea1ec4fda